'''''The Weight of Your Love''''' 是英国乐队[[Editors|Editors]]的第四张录音室唱片，于2013年6月28日由[[PIAS唱片|PIAS唱片]]发行。
首支单曲"A Ton of Love"于2013年5月6日在[[BBC_Radio_1|BBC Radio 1]]广播, 其音乐视频也在当天发布。<ref name="AltSounds">{{cite web |url=http://hangout.altsounds.com/news/158690-editors-unveil-single-a-ton-love-announce.html |title=EDITORS 推出新单曲 'A Ton of Love'并宣布新专辑 – #AltSounds |publisher=Hangout.altsounds.com |date= |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130510012205/http://hangout.altsounds.com/news/158690-editors-unveil-single-a-ton-love-announce.html |archivedate=2013-05-10 |accessdate=2014-03-17 }}</ref>

这是在主音吉他手克里斯·乌尔班诺维奇于2012年4月16日离队后的第一张 Editors 专辑。乐队在官方网站上写道乌尔班诺维奇的离开是因为未来音乐方向不同，并且是友好的。<ref name="NME2">{{cite web |url=http://www.nme.com/news/editors/67870 |title=Editors finally ready to record fourth album | News |publisher=Nme.Com |date=23 December 2012 |accessdate=2014-03-17 |archive-date=2013-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131212120117/http://www.nme.com/news/editors/67870 |dead-url=no }}</ref>这也是新成员贾斯汀·洛基和埃利奥特·威廉姆斯加入后的第一张专辑。<ref name="Best">{{cite web |last=Thane |first=Rich |url=http://www.thelineofbestfit.com/news/latest-news/editors-a-ton-of-love-124845 |title=Editors 命名新专辑, 发布主打单曲 'A Ton of Love' |publisher=The Line of Best Fit |date= |accessdate=2014-03-17 |archive-date=2014-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140317212725/http://www.thelineofbestfit.com/news/latest-news/editors-a-ton-of-love-124845 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

